Usage: set_min_fanout [-help] <fanout_limit> <object_list> [-override]

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
<fanout_limit>            # Value of the minimum fanout load limit constraint
                          # (float, required)
<object_list>             # List of objects: ports, instance pins, library cell
                          # pins or current_design (string, required)
-override                 # Overrides fanout limit from other sources namely
                          # library/constraints (bool, optional)